Innovation Funding Startups Enterprise Partner With Us × Search Pulse 2.0 About Pulse 2.0 Pulse 2.0 is a leading national technology and business news publication located in Ann Arbor, Michigan. We publish important news about the people, products, and companies shaping the future of technology and business. Pulse 2.0 was founded by longtime Forbes technology journalist Amit Chowdhry and software engineer Shan Sadiq. AMIT CHOWDHRY &#8211; PULSE 2.0 CO-FOUNDER &amp; EDITOR IN CHIEF (amit@pulse2.com) LinkedIn Amit, his wife, and their puppy. Amit has written 20,000+ articles about startups, gadgets and large technology companies. Alongside Pulse 2.0, Amit also writes for Forbes . Amit’s Forbes column focuses on the tech economy, startups, and gadgets. SHAN SADIQ &#8211; PULSE 2.0 CO-FOUNDER (shan@pulse2.com) LinkedIn Shan and his nephew. Shan oversees engineering, operations, partnerships, and growth at Pulse 2.0. Pulse 2.0 is growing fast and we&#8217;ve recently moved into our awesome new Ann Arbor office. Drop by and say hi if you&#8217;re ever in the area. We&#8217;re located at 2008 Hogback Road, Suite 2-A, Ann Arbor, MI 48105. PULSE 2.0 STAFF Amit Chowdhry &#8211; Co-Founder &amp; Editor-In-Chief / Contact: amit@pulse2.com /   Twitter / LinkedIn / Forbes Shan Sadiq &#8211; Co-Founder / Contact: shan@pulse2.com / LinkedIn Dan Anderson &#8211; Associate Editor &amp; Business Development Manager / dan@pulse2.com Noah Long &#8211; Associate Editor (Associate Editor &#8211; Venture Capital) / noah@pulse2.com Annie Baker &#8211; Associate Editor (Associate Editor &#8211; Venture Capital)  / annie@pulse2.com Josh Zielinski &#8211; Summer Intern (Associate Editor &#8211; Digital Photography) / Facebook CONTRIBUTORS DJ Miller &#8211; Graduate Student at the University of Tampa David Landau &#8211; Managing Director at ScaleFire Group Enrico Moretti &#8211; Professor at University of California, Berkeley David Murdico &#8211; Executive Creative Director of Supercool Creative Emily Green &#8211; Self-Employed Freelancer in Boston Michael Levin &#8211; New York Times Best Selling Author Riley Kennysmith &#8211; Intern Editor CONTACT INFORMATION Pulse 2.0 LLC 2008 Hogback Rd. Suite 2A Ann Arbor, Michigan 48105 Email: info@pulse2.com Phone: 734-726-0310 Pulse 2.0 is a leading national technology and business news publication located in Ann Arbor, Michigan. FOLLOW US   POPULAR CHANNELS Learn 2.0 Reviews Midwest Tech Women In Tech Leadership M&#038;A Deals Device Specs © 2020 Pulse 2.0 LLC. All rights reserved. About Us Partner With Us Contact Us Terms of Service Privacy Policy 
